{"lemma":"مِيثَرَة","slug":"مِيثَرَة","root":"#.ث.ر","root_slug":"_-ث-ر","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ث-ر","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":1},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n212","n41648"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D9%85%D9%90%D9%8A%D8%AB%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D8%A9"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"a kind of shabrack or saddle-pillow made of silk, or other silk blankets","examples":[{"text":"وَنَهَانَا عَنْ سَبْعٍ، عَنْ خَاتَمِ الذَّهَبِ – أَوْ قَالَ حَلْقَةِ الذَّهَبِ – وَعَنْ لُبْسِ الْحَرِيرِ، وَٱلدِّيبَاجِ، وَٱلسُّنْدُسِ، وَٱلْمَيَاثِرِ.","english":"And he forbade us seven things: to wear golden signets – or golden rings – to wear silk, silk brocade, fine silk or silk saddle-pillows."}]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Tool noun from the root و ث ر (w ṯ r)."},"ipa":["/miː.θa.ra/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n212","headword_ar":"مِيْثَرَةٌ","root":"Avr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tuw^ovuwrN","text_ar":"تُوْثُورٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An iron instrument"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which the bottom of a camel's foot is marked, in order that his footprints upon the ground may be known:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with which the inner"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"under"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"part of a camel's foot is scraped, in order that his footprints may be traced:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K:) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tw^vwr","text_ar":"توثور","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"has a different meaning, explained above, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uvorapN","text_ar":"اُثْرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (M.) The"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miyvarap","text_ar":"مِيثَرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a horse's saddle is without hemz. (S.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K"]},{"entry_id":"n41648","headword_ar":"مِيثَرَةٌ","root":"wvr","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mifoEalapN","text_ar":"مِفْعَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", from"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlwavaArapu","text_ar":"الوَثَارَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) without hemz, (S, TA,) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miwovarapN","text_ar":"مِوْثَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Msb, * TA,) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"w","text_ar":"و"},{"kind":"text","text":"being changed into"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":"because of the kesreh before it, (TA,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waviyrN","text_ar":"وَثِيرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wivorN","text_ar":"وِثْرٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or [only]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miyvarapN","text_ar":"مِيثَرَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA, &c.,) of a horse's saddle, (T, M, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) and of a camel's saddle, (T,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing in the form of a pillow, made for the saddle, like the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Suf~ap","text_ar":"صُفَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.], (M, Mgh, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to render it soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"easy to ride upon:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:) or the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"saddlecloth"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"housing"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"libodap","text_ar":"لِبْدَة"},{"kind":"text","text":") of a horse: (S:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mawaAviru","text_ar":"مَوَاثِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mayaAviru","text_ar":"مَيَاثِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, M, A, Mgh, Msb, K,) the latter agreeing with the sing., (Msb,) retaining the permuted letter, as is the case in"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoyaAdN","text_ar":"اَعْيَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EiydN","text_ar":"عِيدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (IJ, M.) ―         -b2-  Also, accord. to the K, [referring to the three words above,] or [correctly] the red"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mayaAvir","text_ar":"مَيَاثِر"},{"kind":"text","text":", ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmayaAviru AlHumoru","text_ar":"المَيَاثِرُ الحُمْرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) which are forbidden to be used, (S, IAth, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Certain things to ride upon,"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maraAkibu","text_ar":"مَرَاكِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", S, IAth, K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"used by the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEaAjim","text_ar":"اَعَاجِم"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eajam","text_ar":"عَجَم"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAth, TA,) [meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Persians"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other foreigners,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"diybaAj","text_ar":"دِيبَاج"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hariyr","text_ar":"حَرِير"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"silk brocade"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other silk"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, IAth, K, TA:) or the red"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miyvarap","text_ar":"مِيثَرَة"},{"kind":"text","text":", ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"miyvarapu AilA^urojuwaAni","text_ar":"مِيثَرَةُ اِلاُرْجُوَانِ"},{"kind":"text","text":",) forbidden, in a trad., to be used, is"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a stuffed thing to ride upon, which is put upon a camel's saddle:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) and the red"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"myvrp","text_ar":"ميثرة"},{"kind":"text","text":"which is put upon a horse's saddle is included in the prohibition. (IAth, TA.) ―         -b3-  Also, the first of the above three words, (M,) or all of them (K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A garment"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"piece of cloth which is put as a covering over other garments"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of cloth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.) ―         -b4-  Also, (accord. to the K [referring to the three words above,] or [correctly]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mayaAviru","text_ar":"مَيَاثِرُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"skins of beasts of prey."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","A","Mgh","Msb","K","TA","IAth"]}]}}